Calculator
A simple, responsive calculator built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. This project provides basic arithmetic functionalities, including addition, subtraction, multiplication, and division.

Features
Basic arithmetic operations:

Addition

Subtraction

Multiplication

Division

Real-time display of inputs and results.

Clear button to reset the calculator.

Mobile-friendly and responsive design.

Technologies Used
HTML: Used for the structure of the calculator's user interface.

CSS: Used for styling the calculator and making it responsive.

JavaScript: Handles the logic for performing calculations and updating the display.

